by the author to the volume.

I have placed the author attributions primarily using my own
guess about who the principal author is.
I doubt that a commit threshold would give a sensible set of
additional contribution credits.
If the threshold were 10 for example, there would be only a
small number of such attributions, but they would include
crediting both Rob Arthan and Roger Jones with contributions
to USR004 which I'm not convinced is warranted.

Errors in the number of commits shown may have appeared as a result
of attempts to reorganise the table following changes in the proposed assignment
